<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<div
  id="page1"
  class="border-bottom d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
  data-scroll
>
  <div class="px-4 pt-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-body-emphasis mainHeading">
      Welcome To Blog Easy!!
    </h1>
    <div class="my-3 pb-3 mx-auto">
      <p class="lead mb-4">
        Your Own Personal Space To Write And Upload Your Blogs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="py-5 border-bottom mb-3">
  <div class="d-grid gap-1 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
    <button
      type="button"
      onclick="window.location.href='/writeblog'"
      class="btn btn-primary btn-md px-4 me-sm-3"
      fdprocessedid="3goa26"
    >
      Get Started
    </button>
    <button
      type="button"
      onclick="window.location.href='/viewblog'"
      class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-md px-4"
      fdprocessedid="pifia6"
    >
      View Blogs
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page2" class="border-bottom" data-scroll>
  <div class="container">
      <div class="px-4 pt-4">
        <h1
          class="display-5 mt-3 text-center fw-bold text-body-emphasis mainHeading"
        >
          How Does This Website Work?
        </h1>
        <div class="my-3 py-3 centered-paragraphs">
          <p>
            1. You Can Write Blogs By Clicking On Write Blog From Navigation Bar
            or Simply <a href="/writeblog">Click Here!</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            2. Currently You Can Only Add Text Content, But In Later Versions
            You Could Add Links To Text And Images as well.
          </p>
          <p>
            3. After Submitting Your Blog, You May Choose To Write Another Blog
            Or Check Your Blog
          </p>
          <p>4. You Can Edit Or Delete Your Blog Once Submitted</p>
        </div>
      </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div id="page3" class="border-bottom" data-scroll>
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1
      class="display-5 my-3 py-5 text-center fw-bold text-body-emphasis mainHeading"
    >
      Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)
    </h1>

    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeadingOne">
          <button
            class="accordion-button collapsed custom-accordion-button"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#faqCollapseOne"
            aria-expanded="true"
            aria-controls="faqCollapseOne"
          >
            What is BlogEasy?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="faqCollapseOne"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse"
          aria-labelledby="faqHeadingOne"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            BlogEasy is a simple and user-friendly blogging platform where you can create, edit, and delete blogs. It’s designed to give you a seamless writing experience and allows you to share your thoughts or ideas quickly.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeadingTwo">
          <button
            class="accordion-button collapsed custom-accordion-button"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#faqCollapseTwo"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="faqCollapseTwo"
          >
            Why do my blogs disappear after some time?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="faqCollapseTwo"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse"
          aria-labelledby="faqHeadingTwo"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Currently, BlogEasy uses temporary storage, which means your blogs are saved only during your session. Once the session ends or the server is restarted, the blogs are cleared. We’re actively working on integrating a database to ensure your blogs are saved permanently in future updates!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeadingThree">
          <button
            class="accordion-button collapsed custom-accordion-button"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#faqCollapseThree"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="faqCollapseThree"
          >
            Can I edit or delete my blogs?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="faqCollapseThree"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse"
          aria-labelledby="faqHeadingThree"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes! BlogEasy allows you to edit or delete your blogs at any time during your session. Simply navigate to the blog you want to update or remove and use the available options to make changes.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

